Package pqueue.heaps

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MinHeap<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    MinHeaps are complete binary search projects.pqueue.trees whose nodes contents are always smaller than the contents of their children nodes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayMinHeap<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    ArrayMinHeap is a MinHeap implemented using an internal array.
    LinkedMinHeap<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    A LinkedMinHeap is a tree (specifically, a complete binary tree) where every node is smaller than or equal to its descendants (as defined by the Comparable.compareTo(Object) overridings of the type T).
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EmptyHeapException
    A simple Exception that notifies the caller about emptiness of a MinHeap.
